dc_description_s: The hillshade is a black-and-white image showing elevation changes in the landscape. It is created from a digital elevation model as if the elevation surface were illuminated by a hypothetical light source shining from the northwest.
dc_creator_sm: Minnesota Department of Natural Resources and Minnesota Geospatial Information Office
dc_relation_sm: For more information about elevation data for Minnesota, see: http://www.mngeo.state.mn.us/chouse/elevation/index.html
